309
00:13:33,800 --> 00:13:34,880
About a week ago.

310
00:13:37,520 --> 00:13:38,080
Oh my god.

311
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:39,960
I just remembered,

312
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:41,800
