366
00:15:46,040 --> 00:15:47,480
In that game,

367
00:15:48,280 --> 00:15:50,360
Lin Ran was the first to fall to his death,

368
00:15:50,360 --> 00:15:52,490
then Li Xiaoru was the second to drown.

369
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:56,000
Finally, Zhao Wenbing and Xu Xing died too.

370
00:15:56,520 --> 00:15:57,000
Now,

371
00:15:57,560 --> 00:15:59,690
